headline: Should You Invest in NextEra (NEE) Based on Bullish Wall Street Views?
summary: The average brokerage recommendation (ABR) for NextEra (NEE) is equivalent to a Buy. The overly optimistic recommendations of Wall Street analysts make the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric questionable. So, is it worth buying the stock?
